snippet.title: Glory of the Roman Empire - gameplay
snippet.description:
Glory of the Roman Empire is a nice city builder for beginners. Easy to play and master.

RIG:
CPU Athlon64 4000+ (single core - San Diego)
GPU ATI Radeon HD4670 512 DDR3 HIS TURBO IceQ
RAM 2gb PC3200
Win XP
